This file stores local/development environment variables.

DO NOT COMMIT THIS FILE TO GIT. Add it to your .gitignore file!

Node environment (development or production)
NODE_ENV=development

Firebase Configuration (only needed for local development with Firestore)
Uncomment to use Firestore in development instead of in-memory storage
# USE_FIRESTORE=false
# FIREBASE_CONFIG={"type":"service_account","project_id":"..."}

Port the Express server runs on (Cloud Run will ignore this but it's good for local testing)
PORT=5000
